-- Atlantic Grupa 1st-Half Net Falls to 6.6 Million Kuna
-- B y   J a s m i n a   K u z m a n o v i c
-- 2012-07-30T10:12:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-30/atlantic-grupa-1st-half-net-falls-to-6-6-million-kuna-correct-.html
(Corrects net figure in first paragraph.)  Atlantic Grupa (ATGRRA)  d.d., a Croatian soft
drink maker and distributor, said its net income in the first
half fell to 6.6 million kuna from 14.5 million kuna in the same
period a year earlier.  The Zagreb-based company also said today that revenue was
up 6.6 percent to 2.3 billion kuna and earnings before interest,
taxes, depreciation and amortization rose 24.8 percent to 282
million kuna.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jasmina Kuzmanovic in Zagreb at 
 jkuzmanovic@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  